                    <div style="width:100%; clear:both; padding-top:5px;">
    <div class="boxtitle bluetext" style="margin-left:5px; font-weight:bold;">Announcements</div>
      <div id="announcements" style="clear:both;"> 


  <div style="margin-top:10px; text-align:left;">
 <strong><p>On 29 August 2013, Member States agreed during open-ended informal consultations in New York on the nomination of H.E. Dr. Zahir Tanin, Ambassador, Permanent Representative of Afghanistan to the United Nations was nominated as the Chair designate of the "Fifth Biennial Meeting of States to Consider Implementation of the Programme of Action to Prevent, Combat and Eradicate the Illicit Trade in Small Arms and Light Weapons in All Its Aspects," (BMS5) tentatively scheduled for 16 – 20 June 2014. </p></strong>
   </div>

  <!--div style="margin-top:10px; text-align:left;">
 <a href="http://www.un.org/en/events/againstnucleartestsday/2013/events.shtml" target="_blank">Tentative programme of the Informal Meeting of the UN General Assembly to mark the Observance of the International Day against Nuclear Tests &mdash; 5 September 2013</a> 
   </div>
   
   <div style="margin-top:10px; text-align:left;">
<a href= "http://www.un.org/ga/search/view_doc.asp?symbol=CTBT-Art.XIV/2013/INF.1"target="_blank">Information note for all participants for the Conference on Facilitating The Entry Into Force of the Comprehensive Nuclear-Test-Ban Treaty.</a>
</div>                  
 
          
        
          
                      <!--div style=" margin-top:10px; text-align:left;">
                      
                 <p><b>Fraud notice:</b> The United Nations Office for Disarmament Affairs (UNODA) has been made aware of various email correspondences, falsely stating that they are issued by, or in association with UNODA, the United Nations and/or its officials. These scams, which may seek to obtain money and/or in many cases personal details from the recipients of such correspondence, are fraudulent. If you are the recipient of such an email, please forward it, with complete headers, to <a href="mailto://unoda-web@un.org">unoda-web@un.org</a>.</p>
